        <h2>What Is Feier?</h2>
        <p class="about-description">
            Feier is an event planning platform designed to connect nearby communities through organized events hosted on our website.
            If distance is a problem for some, we offer the option of virtual events to connect those across seas, states, or cities.
            Whether you're hosting a small gathering or coordinating a large-scale conference, Feier provides all the tools you need
            in one intuitive platform. We emphasize full creative control to each of our users, we host the event on our website and
            you can design everythign yourself or you can pick one of our templates. Need help? Just ask our AI chatbot Francesca, she'll
            be able to help you with any questions!
        </p>
